[{"id":"f2d4f35530aab7c6e69ddb7425e8b951","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"from Anthony Barrett","date":"2008-06-27T12:37:07.000Z","formatted_date":"Jun 27, 2008","formatted_time":"12:37 PM","body":" \n\n \n\nFrom: OSSA1@aol.com [mailto:OSSA1@aol.com] \nSent: Wednesday, June 25, 2008 3:50 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: For JE\n\n \n\nHi Jeffrey,\n\n \n\nI just spoke to Nadja who gave me the news.  I would like to see you but\nI understand that you have many important issues to take care of.  I\nwould just like to say that I will always remember the opportunities you\nhave given me and my family and know exactly the caring, thoughtful and\ngenerous person you are.  I will never forget.  If there is anything you\nneed taken care of or any help with anything I am available for you\nanytime.\n\n \n\nBest wishes and thoughts \n\n \n\nAnthony\n\n\n\n\n\n________________________________\n\nGas prices getting you down? Search AOL Autos for fuel-efficient used\ncars <http://autos.aol.com/used?ncid=aolaut00050000000007> .\n\n","body_html":"<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:m=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\n\n<head>\n<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Content-Type\" CONTENT=\"text/html; charset=us-ascii\">\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 12 (filtered medium)\">\n<!--[if !mso]>\n<style>\nv\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\no\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\nw\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n.shape {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n<style>\n<!--\n /* Font Definitions */\n @font-face\n\t{font-family:Calibri;\n\tpanose-1:2 15 5 2 2 2 4 3 2 4;}\n@font-face\n\t{font-family:Tahoma;\n\tpanose-1:2 11 6 4 3 5 4 4 2 4;}\n /* Style Definitions */\n p.M