;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>I&nbsp;just spoke to Nadja who gave me the news.&nbsp; I would\nlike to see you but I understand that you have many important issues to take\ncare of.&nbsp; I would just like to say that I will always remember the\nopportunities you have given me and my family and know exactly the&nbsp;caring,\nthoughtful and generous person you are.&nbsp; I will never forget.&nbsp; If\nthere is anything you need taken care of or any help with anything I am\navailable for you anytime.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>Best wishes and thoughts <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>Anthony<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:12.0pt'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'><br>\n<br>\n<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<div>\n\n<div class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:7.5pt;text-align:center'><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>\n\n<hr size=2 width=\"100%\" align=center>\n\n</span></div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.5pt'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>Gas prices getting you down?\nSearch AOL Autos for fuel-efficient <a\nhref=\"http://autos.aol.com/used?ncid=aolaut00050000000007\" tar